snippet.title: The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos is now available! Get ready to start this awesome quest and take control of a party of less-than-qualified adventurers! The strangest of all dungeons is ready for you; the question is, are you ready for it?

The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos is a wacky tactical RPG, centered around the story of a group of very dumb adventurers. Utilizing the strengths and weaknesses of every member of the party, guide them towards their goal!

Get The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/970830/The_Dungeon_Of_Naheulbeuk_The_Amulet_Of_Chaos/
Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/the-dungeon-of-naheulbeuk/home
GOG.com: https://www.gog.com/game/the_dungeon_of_naheulbeuk_the_amulet_of_chaos

Follow Dear Villagers for more information on The Amulet of Chaos:
On Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DearVillagers
On Twitter: https://twitter.com/DearVillagers
